<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #171717;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .reset-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #171717;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .reset-button:hover {
            background-color: #171717;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #888888;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666666;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= username %>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your password for your <%= appName %> account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
            <p>To reset your password, click the button below:</p>
            <a href="<%= resetPasswordURL %>" class="reset-button">Reset Password</a>
            <p class="expiry-notice">This password reset link will expire in 10 Minutes.</p>
            <p>If you're having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:</p>
            <p><%= resetPasswordURL %></p>
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>